{"type": "article", "id": 25247, "title": "纸片浮雕", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185829LVIygHsPk6hZwjNF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">英国视觉设计师 Matt Lee 用纸片做了这组浮雕作品。他用了同样颜色的纸张以不同形状相互叠加或相错，拼出了有浮雕效果的图案。可以看到纸张之间的凹凸纹路，在光影照射下形成了浅浅的阴影，很有层次。图案看起来有点抽象实则非常细腻，<a href=\"http://www.matt-lee.com/death-landscapes-3\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185825UojsCJfiBd24F1cE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185826ut62gL3RsVYrIiUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185826wxNSD6LUom0JWYlv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185827ivFVOle4CwWAcMGI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607185828QE9fSktC5Po3Wz8Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071858280KhuikIbjOQNZlwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}